casebody.data:
Edson Gillette, Appellant, v. Robert E. Allen et al., Respondents.

Reported below, 264 App. Div. 599.

Submitted November 23, 1942; decided December 10, 1942. Oscar J. Brown for motion. Bertram D. Hummel and J. Norman Crannage opposed.

Motion dismissed, with ten dollars costs and necessary printing disbursements on the ground that the order does' not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
